menu "CamperNode OS"

    config CAMPER_OTA_BASE_FIRMWARE
        bool "OTA base firmware (v0.1.1, no MOSFET :Od)"
        default n
        help
            Build the one-time USB base image: Zigbee OTA client enabled,
            GPIO-Karte :Od (MOSFET) disabled. Flash this once, then OTA to
            the full firmware (0.2.0+) for MOSFET support.

endmenu
